title: Fantastic Four Vol. 1: Imaginauts (Trade Paperback)
description: As Waid & Wieringo are redefining Doctor Doom in the monthly series, get on board their run from the beginning. Learn the truth behind Mister Fantastic's decision to turn his friends into the Fantastic Four. See our heroes face off against a sentient mathematical equation driven mad by love, an infestation of insects from another dimension, a cascading wave of molecular instability, and the Thing on a homicidal rampage that only the Human Torch can stop. Collecting FANTASTIC FOUR Vol. 3, #60-66; and #56 (a special Thing solo tale).
